# Sarana Omni - Project Overview

This is a **Sarana Omni** Next.js application - an intelligent omnichannel communication platform that integrates WhatsApp to simplify and enhance customer support services for businesses.

## Technology Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15.3.1 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript 5
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4
- **UI Components**: Headless UI, Lucide React icons
- **Authentication**: Cookie-based with middleware protection
- **State Management**: React hooks and context
- **Build Tool**: Turbopack for development

## Project Structure
```
├── app/                    # Next.js App Router pages
│   ├── dashboard/         # Protected dashboard area
│   ├── login/            # Authentication pages
│   ├── register/         
│   └── (other routes)/   
├── components/            # Reusable React components
│   ├── ai-agent/         # AI-related components
│   └── layout/           # Layout components
├── services/             # API service layer
├── types/                # TypeScript type definitions
├── helpers/              # Utility functions
├── providers/            # React context providers
└── public/              # Static assets
```

## Key Features
- User authentication and registration
- Dashboard with protected routes
- AI agent integration
- PDF processing capabilities
- Omnichannel communication tools
- WhatsApp integration

The project follows modern Next.js 13+ patterns with server and client components, TypeScript for type safety, and a clean service layer architecture.
